# External References

This directory contains external documentation in LLM-friendly formats.

## Contents

Store here:
- Third-party API documentation
- Framework references
- Library guides
- Protocol specifications

## Naming Convention

`tool-name-llms.txt` — LLM-optimized documentation
`tool-name-reference.md` — Markdown reference docs

## Keeping Current

- Note the version/date when adding references
- Update when upgrading dependencies
- Remove when dependencies are dropped

